{"tid":2374091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【拜登就職】克林頓疑在拜登演說期間睡着","createTime":"2021-01-21T03:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T04:49:06.000Z","uid":24660,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c4087ffa3973af9e206e2f044e56e4ef207939","tid":2374091,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dn0wTokUQS9YW4qsDEusz9SwrnA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UZZUGAIJBZHMBO7Y33YVHHOCFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fdn0wTokUQS9YW4qsDEusz9SwrnA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUZZUGAIJBZHMBO7Y33YVHHOCFQ.jpg&h=f39fd17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n74歲的克林頓比拜登還要年輕近4年，他卸任總統後亦出席全數6次總統就職典禮。不過電視畫面可見，克林頓在周三拜登演說期間看來不慎睡着，未知是否因社交距離措施影響，導致他距離講台太遠而分心。克林頓身旁的妻子兼前國務卿希拉莉，以至他身前的前副總統彭斯則未受影響，繼續聆聽拜登演說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210121/Z3JBR3VL5BH5TL6NTTFDU4ZSVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210121%2FZ3JBR3VL5BH5TL6NTTFDU4ZSVY%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=2b8f0512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210121%2FZ3JBR3VL5BH5TL6NTTFDU4ZSVY%2F&h=751eb490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210121/Z3JBR3VL5BH5TL6NTTFDU4ZSVY/</a>"},{"pid":"af8b819a7b523e0c3ce785d65a16eaddef57eb59","tid":2374091,"uid":14422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"冇靚女係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1383b0c07bdba04ff68329df8c89f37a8c780a7e","tid":2374091,"uid":85461,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.th